description:
iJO1366*
This model is based on iJO1366 [1], but enhanced with enzyme constraints according to the sMOMENT method using AutoPACMEN [2]. This model is also published in [2]. The protein pool pseudo-reaction is called ER_pool_TG_ (its upper bound defines the total protein amount per dry biomass) and the protein pool pseudo-metabolite is called prot_pool.
[1] https://doi.org/10.1038/msb.2011.65 
[2] https://doi.org/10.1186/s12859-019-3329-9
